text: Phrynetoides minor is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bernhard Schwarzer in 1931. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo and Uganda.BioLib.cz - Phrynetoides minor. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1931
